      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TURBO TATE (3) has been settling off the speed lately, finishing sixth (23.05) last time in a Grade 5/6 at this track. Solid record at the distance winning two races. Has ability and is a key runner. MYSTIC PIXEL (1) charged out of the boxes with a slick early split and went straight to the front, giving a huge sight but headed late when a nose second (22.87) over 400m at this track. Expected to be in this for a long way. BLACKPOOL VIPER (7) collided with another runner and was out of the placings when a 4 length fifth (17.72) in a Grade 6 at this track. Has the ability and can measure up. TWO TRUTHS (8) missed the placings here last start but is well-placed to atone.",
